Android IAP receipt verification
Skip to end of metadata
Created by Yoshi Miyamoto, last modified on May 23, 2016 Go to start of metadata
user's receipt will be verified with android key which can be obtained from Google Developer Console, signature found in user receipt with PyCrypto 
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/5440550/verifying-signature-on-android-in-app-purchase-message-in-python-on-google-app-e
pycypto
https://www.dlitz.net/software/pycrypto/api/current/
Dev, Staging, Production use this. no separate verification method for each environment. 